00:26:01.750 --> 00:26:04.490
sell out because she said "Buy the book."

00:26:04.490 --> 00:26:10.500
In an Oprah-less world, what you want to do
is, New York Times is the touchstone in terms

00:26:10.500 --> 00:26:15.230
of newspapers and this was the cover review
a few weeks ago [baby giggles]

00:26:15.230 --> 00:26:17.590
&gt;&gt;male #6: sorry
&gt;&gt;Larry Tye: in the the New York Times and

