00:29:30.029 --> 00:29:40.350
for his 75th, so you actually want to be the
definitive one that we sell before and then

00:29:40.350 --> 00:29:51.010
your paperback comes out a year later [laughter]
and the paperback will come out just in time

00:29:51.010 --> 00:29:52.010
for that.

